data.description: This stunning 2-story home, nestled in the prestigious Regents Park neighborhood, boasts a range of exquisite features. The main level welcomes you with beautiful hardwood floors that flow seamlessly throughout. Convenience is key with a 1st-floor laundry room and an attached 3-car garage, offering both style and practicality. As you explore this luxurious residence, you'll notice the attention to detail with crown molding, tray ceilings, and a cozy fireplace in the family room. A wet bar and bay windows add a touch of sophistication. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample space for meal preparation. It seamlessly connects to the family room, creating an ideal gathering place. The formal living room and dining room are elegantly appointed and can be separated by beautiful pocket doors. The open-concept design of the main floor is perfect for both entertaining and everyday living. Upstairs, you'll find 5 spacious bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. The master bedroom is a true retreat with a private en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. This level offers comfort and privacy for the entire family. Outside, the professionally landscaped yard complements the wooded lot, creating a picturesque setting. This home is a true gem in an esteemed neighborhood, offering the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to make this property your dream home.
